# Keep LF on files that break with CRLF: shell-script shebangs on Unix/in Linux
# containers (dev.sh, deploy/backup.sh) and Make recipes (GNU make mishandles the
# trailing CR). Scoped narrowly on purpose: no blanket `* text=auto`, to avoid
# renormalizing unrelated files.
*.sh     text eol=lf
Makefile text eol=lf
